| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1263 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 23e7a30e-62f1-5f07-bf62-4897d8585c53"
